 <name>Gtk+ UVC Viewer</name>
 <summary>capture video from v4l2 devices</summary>
 <description>
  <p>Video capture tool for video4linux2 compliant cameras, with special emphasis on the linux uvc driver. It provides Image (jpg, png, bmp) and Video (mjpeg, flv1, wmv1, mpg2, mpg4,...) capture with sound in several formats( currently: avi and matroska). I also supports a control panel option (--control_only) that is compatible with any other v4l2 app.</p>
 </description>
